title: Ep 1042 - The Courts Order
shortDesc: Jethalal comes running to Taarak as he gets a letter from the court. When Taarak reads, he informs Taarak that they will have to visit their lawyer. Is Jethalal in big trouble? Watch the episode to find out.

title: Ep. 1043 - Jetha's Court Case - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha walks down to see all the people of gokuldham waiting for him. They all gathered to wish him and Daya and stand by them during the trial. Jetha is moved by all the love and support given by the people.

title: Ep. 1044 - A Gathering At The Court - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha reaches the court but he is very nervous. All the people from Gokuldham gathered at the court to support Jetha. Some seem to be very supportive and some not so much.

title: Ep. 1045 - Gokuldham Against The Judge - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: At the court, Soudi gets furious and argues with the Judge. Jetha and the others try to calm him down. But he makes a scene and leaves the court.

title: Ep. 1046 - Daya's Confession - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The Judge asks Daya about the party and she decides to tell them the truth. The lawyer twists her answer and she gets furious. All the people of Gokuldham rage in anger.

title: Ep. 1047 - Champaklal's Anger - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: A few people reveal Jetha's wrong doings in front of the Judge. Champaklal gets furious and scolds Jetha. Daya stands up for Jetha.

title: Ep. 1048 - Finding A Solution - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The people of Gokuldham gather to find a solution for Jetha's problem. Everyone shares their idea's and come up with a solution.

title: Ep. 1049 - Popatlal Becomes A Detective - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal argues with the Jetha's might-be wife. Jetha is upset and tries to sort out the issue. They decide if they should call the police to Gokuldham.

title: Ep. 1050 - Jetha's Spoiled Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha is very troubled and decides to visit the lawyer with Tarak. He explains his problems to the lawyer. Later he gets the news that his name is spoiled because of the case.

title: Ep. 1051 - Jetha Brings Home His Bride - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Everyone gathers to help Jetha. Meanwhile, Jetha brings home his new bride. Everyone is shocked. Daya decides to leave Jetha's house and Tapu wants to go with her.

title: Ep. 1052 - Missing Jetha - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha is missing from Gokuldham. Meanwhile, Gulabri is preparing for the wedding to happen at Gokuldham. Everyone is searching for Jethalal.

title: Ep. 1053 - Jetha Becomes A Monk - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha returns and shows up as a monk. This is Jetha's great plan to avoid marrying another women. Everyone is shocked and scolds Jetha.

title: Ep. 1054 - Jetha's Decision - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Everyone is furious at Jetha and asks him not to go away. But Jetha keeps up his acting and tries to leave. Is Jetha

title: Ep. 1055 - The Ultimate Blackmail - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha tries to leave but Gulabo stops him and blackmails him. She tells everyone that she'll kill herself if Jetha leaves. Everyone is stunned.

title: Ep. 1056 - Gulabo Agrees - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: After a lot of convincing from everybody, Gulabo agrees to marry and the people of Gokuldham are ready to celebrate and enjoy this moment.
